  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3815328">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3815328/" class="title-link">民主虽然是个好东西，消化不良可不太好</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3815328"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/cxmin/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1346048-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/cxmin/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">锦翼</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-10-04"
      class="main-meta">2010-10-04 18:31:50</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3815328_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      在读这本书之前，我关于拉丁美洲的了解，大都来自高中学的世界近代史，知道是玻利瓦尔领导拉丁美洲独立，记得高考的时候有一道历史题，大意是为什么拉丁美洲独立后没有像美国那样富强起来。我隐约记得我是一通发挥，其中一条是因为美国是被英国一个国际在蹂躏，而拉丁美洲...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3815328/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">7有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
